#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The full documentation for &kmymoney; is maintained as a docbook manual. "
#| "If the &khelpcenter; program is properly installed at your site, the "
#| "command <userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> <parameter>help:/"
